# Keep the build context small and SECRET-FREE.

# Dependencies / build output (reinstalled / recompiled inside the image).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets and local state must NEVER enter the image.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
.cache/
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite-*
**/*.db
**/*.db-*
**/*-journal
**/*.log

# VCS / CI / tooling / docs not needed at runtime.
.git
.github
.claude
scripts
docs
*.md

# NOTE: the `frontend` source IS part of the build context now — the image builds
# the SPA and serves it alongside the API. Its node_modules / dist are still
# excluded above (**/node_modules, **/dist), and secrets/DB/cache never enter.
